      "text": "ちょっと、泣き過ぎよ。しっかりしなさい\n……どうだったかしら？　私達の新曲",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ don't cry too much. Pull yourself together.\n…So‚ what did you think? Our new song",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5333249133,
      "endTime": 29.9429845851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
