      "text": "昔、遙子さんとお姉ちゃんで\n密かに作っていた曲なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a song Haruko-san and big sister\nsecretly worked on in the past.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8333249133,
      "endTime": 38.793324760699996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
