      "text": "未完成だった曲をみんなで完成させました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We completed the unfinished song together",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9999915799,
      "endTime": 42.677315922599995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
