      "text": "この曲には、歌っている私達以外の想いも乗せています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This song carries not only our voices but also the hearts of others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8666582466,
      "endTime": 47.335343206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
