      "text": "日頃の感謝、出会えたことの感謝\n一緒に過ごしてきたその全ての時間が宝物です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gratitude for everyday life‚ gratitude for meeting each other\nAll the time we spent together is a treasure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5333249133,
      "endTime": 55.4926447909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
